# AI Support Triage System (n8n + OpenAI)

A lightweight automation engine that classifies, prioritizes, and routes incoming support tickets using AI. Built to replace manual Tier 1 triage with a scalable, API-driven workflow.

---

## 🚀 Overview

Support teams lose significant time on repetitive ticket classification and routing. This system automates the first layer of support operations:

- Detects intent from raw tickets
- Assigns priority levels
- Categorizes issues (billing, API, bug, general)
- Generates a suggested response
- Outputs structured JSON for downstream systems

Designed for integration into modern support stacks (Zendesk, Intercom, custom CRMs, Slack workflows).

---

## 🧠 Core Capabilities

- Real-time ticket ingestion via webhook
- AI-powered intent classification
- Priority scoring (P0–P3)
- Structured response generation
- Optional escalation logic
- Clean JSON output for automation pipelines

